WEBVTT

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:06.000
Well, good afternoon family. Thank you

00:00:03.679 --> 00:00:07.600
for joining us again today.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.960
We're going to go ahead and pray. We're

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:10.320
going to go over some of the things the

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:13.360
Lord showed us last time we were

00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:15.599
together. We're going to show

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:19.198
you some things that are in the news

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:21.680
that are, I believe,

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:23.519
confirmations to the visions the Lord

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:25.359
has given us. We don't want to be flaky

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:27.759
here. And I'm going to tell you right

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:29.679
off the bat, everything that we do on

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:33.600
this channel, I give all the glory to

00:00:29.679 --> 00:00:35.440
God. We had a viral video on TikTok.

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:37.120
I thought it was on YouTube, but YouTube

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:39.440
pulled it down. They didn't want me

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:40.879
talking about it on YouTube, so YouTube

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:44.079
pulled it and wouldn't even let me

00:00:40.879 --> 00:00:44.718
upload it. But TikTok, it got

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:52.800
2.7 million hits in

00:00:50.399 --> 00:00:57.280
the last three days.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:01:00.078
2.7 million. That's a lot for us. And

00:00:57.280 --> 00:01:03.359
that's exciting to have that many people

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:05.199
clicking on TikTok,

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:07.200
Instagram, and stuff like that.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:10.798
Braden said, 'Dad, that was amazing

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:12.880
what the Lord did with that.'And so

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:14.560
we give all the glory to God and all

00:01:12.880 --> 00:01:16.158
that we say in word and deed, we give

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:19.759
all to the glory of God. And I want you

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:22.240
to know, we attracted the to deflect

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:25.840
every single time. But it's exciting

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:27.360
because to use somebody like me—that

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:29.840
God would say, 'Hey, Brandon, I'm

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:32.799
going to use you in these last days'—I was

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:34.159
a janitor for 15 years, and didn't think

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:36.240
I was ever going to stop being a

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:38.799
janitor. And the Lord said, 'I want you

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:41.119
to go on YouTube and

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:44.400
I'll show you things to come,

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:46.079
and your main job is to pray. Your main

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:47.840
job is to pray.'People say, 'Are you

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:50.240
prophetic? Are you this? Are you that?'I am

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:52.159
just a prayer warrior. I just

00:01:50.240 --> 00:01:54.720
feel like that's what my main mission

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:58.399
has always been. And as I was driving

00:01:54.720 --> 00:02:00.560
down the road yesterday, and I was

00:01:58.399 --> 00:02:02.399
going to get the parts for the septic

00:02:02.399 --> 00:02:05.920
tank and all the things that I

00:02:03.759 --> 00:02:08.239
told you about just a little bit ago—because

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:10.720
my heart's always been

00:02:08.239 --> 00:02:12.959
healing evangelism like Billy Burke. I

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:14.480
wanted that my whole life since I've

00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:16.480
been a kid. I watched Benny Hinn and

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:17.840
all these others,

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:22.400
seeing people fall out

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:25.200
and be touched by the Holy Ghost.

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:27.599
I would read and listen to

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:29.679
books about Smith Wigglesworth and all

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:31.920
these greats like John G. Lake, and I

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:34.959
thought, 'Lord, use me for that.'And I know

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:36.559
that's coming—healings

00:02:34.959 --> 00:02:39.680
and demonstrations and

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:42.319
manifestations of the glory—but as I was

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:44.959
driving down the road, the Lord said to

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:47.518
me, 'You've not yielded fully to what I've

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:50.760
asked you to do. You're still

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:50.760
split.'I

00:02:50.959 --> 00:02:55.280
said, 'What are you talking about?'and

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:59.679
I'm praying in the spirit and I

00:02:55.280 --> 00:03:02.159
started weeping.

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:04.319
I said, 'You're right.

00:03:02.159 --> 00:03:08.319
I'm running.

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:10.079
I don't mind doing this for you,

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:11.920
this prayer part,

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:15.519
but it's not where my heart's

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:19.119
at. My heart is to see the sick

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:21.440
healed. My heart is to do a ministry

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:23.680
like Billy Burke.'But

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:26.800
he said,

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:30.799
'Brandon, I need you.'He said, 'Do you

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:34.640
feel like you know better than me?'I

00:03:30.799 --> 00:03:38.400
said, 'Well, I don't. My heart is no,

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:40.640
but my actions are yes.'You

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:42.400
know, like I

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:43.920
know in my head

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:45.760
I'm not better than you,

00:03:43.920 --> 00:03:48.958
but in me I feel like,

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:51.200
well, maybe I can convince Him otherwise

00:03:48.959 --> 00:03:53.760
to do healing ministry.

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:55.839
But He said,

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:59.359
'Do you not know that this is the

00:03:55.840 --> 00:04:01.360
foundation for the healing revival?

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:04.760
This is the foundation. The prayer has

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:04.760
to come

00:04:05.627 --> 00:04:08.239
first.'He

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:10.319
said, 'You don't know better than me,

00:04:08.239 --> 00:04:13.280
and I know how to get it done before you

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:15.679
do. Would you just yield to what I've

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:19.440
asked you to do?

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:21.358
Stop being double, going this way in

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:26.160
your heart and doing this. Yield

00:04:21.358 --> 00:04:27.840
completely to what I've called you to do

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:30.840
and then a mantle will come on you

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.840
stronger.'When

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:39.680
He said it, it was

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:43.039
like you get gut-punched. I

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:47.840
just sat there and I went, 'Ah.'So

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:52.080
I told Diana, I said, 'I repent

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:56.159
because I have been so divided in myself.'This

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:58.080
is a lot of pressure. And I

00:04:56.160 --> 00:05:00.720
never looked at healing evangelism as

00:04:58.080 --> 00:05:03.280
pressure, which it probably is when you

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:04.880
step into it, but whenever

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:06.799
you're doing this and you're praying for

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:08.560
the nations and you're going through the

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:10.639
motions of this, this has been a lot of

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:14.403
work. And He said to me, 'I want you to

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:16.800
yield completely to it.'And

00:05:14.403 --> 00:05:19.039
so I made a vow. I said,

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:21.039
'I'll do everything I can as

00:05:19.039 --> 00:05:24.400
much as my heart is on

00:05:21.039 --> 00:05:28.320
the healing side, and I'll do it. But

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:30.880
to give myself completely over to prayer,

00:05:28.320 --> 00:05:34.000
to give myself over without having

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:36.320
that split of thinking I want to do

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:38.880
this while I'm asking

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:41.360
you to do that—this is what I'm asking

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:43.199
you to do: raise up a million-man and woman

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:46.080
prayer army.'And I say it out of

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:48.560
my mouth, but my heart's not there.

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:50.400
I'll go, 'Yeah, we're raising up a million-man and woman

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:53.600
prayer army,'and we

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:56.560
have a lot of people show up every week

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:58.320
from all over the world and

00:05:56.560 --> 00:06:00.880
get hundreds of people saved, but my

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:02.800
heart is always over here. I'm looking

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:04.319
over there in the pasture, and

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:08.319
the Lord said, 'I want you

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:12.319
to be right here.'And so, as I was

00:06:08.319 --> 00:06:13.759
driving down the road, He spoke to me

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:16.560
because I was asking, 'What's

00:06:13.759 --> 00:06:19.280
going on, Lord?'because I'm always

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:22.000
checking my thermostat spiritually. Are

00:06:19.280 --> 00:06:24.318
you all in? Are you okay with the

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:26.400
Father? Is everything good with the

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:29.039
Lord? Where are

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:32.560
you at with Him? And I'm always checking

00:06:29.039 --> 00:06:34.560
that thermostat. And when He corrected it,

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:37.039
because when I crossed over from the

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:38.720
Fourth of July and this week, I

00:06:37.039 --> 00:06:40.240
was praying over things and that's what

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:41.600
His message was. He was talking to me

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:44.800
about it. So, I always try to tell you

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:47.600
where I'm at and what's going on. I want to

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:50.240
inspire you to have a fresh relationship

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:53.440
with the Lord. I want you to have a

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:55.600
fresh experience that's real. It's not some

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:58.000
religious experience that your grandma

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:59.919
told you about. God is an

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:02.800
ever-present help in a time of need, and

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:05.520
He wants to be your friend. He wants to

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:08.639
talk to you about everything. The moment

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:11.198
you yield to Him, even with partial yield,

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:13.599
look what He's done. But He said, 'I want

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:15.599
this to come. I want this to be even

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:18.000
greater in the days ahead, but you've got

00:07:15.599 --> 00:07:20.880
to not be divided in your heart toward

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:25.039
it. Yield completely to what I've called

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:28.400
you to do and embrace it. Pull it in. And

00:07:25.039 --> 00:07:32.000
when it's time—and I know when it's time—I'll

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:34.159
let you do something different.'You

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:36.479
can remember I told you, being a

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:38.080
janitor, I said it all the time.

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:40.080
He said, 'I want you to stop

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:42.719
complaining about cleaning the bathrooms,'because

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:44.719
every day I'd say, 'I hate doing this. I

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:47.280
hate cleaning these toilets. I don't

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:49.919
want to clean 92 toilets

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:53.159
four times a

00:07:49.919 --> 00:07:53.159
week.'So

00:07:53.570 --> 00:07:57.360
He said, 'You've got to stop

00:07:55.599 --> 00:07:59.520
complaining.'He

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:01.919
goes, 'When you stop complaining and

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:05.520
yield to what I've called you to do,

00:08:01.919 --> 00:08:05.520
I'll release you from it.

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:12.240
Die to it.'So year after year, it took

00:08:09.919 --> 00:08:14.318
me forever just to stop complaining with

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:16.639
my mouth.

00:08:14.319 --> 00:08:18.639
And I said, 'I'm not

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:22.639
complaining anymore.'He said, 'Yeah,

00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:25.520
you are. Your heart's full of it.'He

00:08:22.639 --> 00:08:27.120
said, 'I'm looking at the inward man.

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:29.198
You may not say it with your mouth and

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:32.080
complain to Diana anymore, but you

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:33.279
complain in your heart to me.'He said,

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:36.479
'You're going to have to do that.'I

00:08:33.279 --> 00:08:37.838
said, 'I'm going to be here forever.

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:40.800
I'm going to be doing this for the rest

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:43.519
of my life.'And He said, 'No,

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:45.359
you won't. Just keep going and give me

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:47.680
thanks and glory for everything I've

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:49.680
done. All that you do in word, give

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:52.319
all glory to God. Give Him thanks and

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:54.319
give Him praise for it.'So, I cleaned

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:56.560
those bathrooms and every single one, 'Oh,

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:59.040
Father, I thank you for every one of

00:08:56.560 --> 00:09:01.599
these toilets. I thank you that the

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:03.519
people

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:04.880
coming in here want to

00:09:03.519 --> 00:09:06.720
see a clean bathroom. They don't want to

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:08.480
see poo on a stool.

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:10.399
Father, I thank you, Lord,

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:12.240
that the souls that are coming here

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:14.160
are going to be blessed.'And I would

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:17.120
just sit there and praise Him every

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:18.959
single time I cleaned those bathrooms.

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:21.600
When the kids threw up on the floor or

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:22.959
whatever, I cleaned it up. 'Oh God, I thank You,'I'd

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.160
say in my heart. I

00:09:22.959 --> 00:09:26.959
didn't have to be radical and let

00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:28.959
everybody else hear me. You

00:09:26.959 --> 00:09:30.319
don't have to be weird and flaky. But I

00:09:28.959 --> 00:09:33.359
said it in my heart and I praised

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:36.800
Him. And then one day,

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:38.800
He said, 'You're done.'I

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:40.319
said, 'Done with what?'He said,

00:09:38.800 --> 00:09:43.760
'Your assignment

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:45.360
here. You're released. You can move on. You stopped

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:47.279
complaining in your heart.'And

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:50.000
I didn't even realize that I

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:52.480
did. I started to

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:54.880
love what I was doing; I started to

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:56.640
embrace it. And I said, 'God, if I do

00:09:54.880 --> 00:10:00.720
this for the rest of my life, I'm okay

00:09:56.640 --> 00:10:03.040
with it.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:06.000
We are cleaning and I'm actually

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:08.079
having fun with it.'How do you have fun

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:09.600
being a janitor and cleaning 90-something toilets

00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:14.480
four times a week?

00:10:11.839 --> 00:10:16.480
Saturdays, Sundays, Wednesdays,

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:18.800
and then again on

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:20.480
Sunday afternoon. You keep it

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:22.160
clean because

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:25.920
you have 10,000 people come through; it

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:28.399
gets nasty.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:32.479
All that to be said,

00:10:28.399 --> 00:10:35.600
God

00:10:32.480 --> 00:10:37.839
released me. But it came out of

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:40.399
when I was dead to it and

00:10:37.839 --> 00:10:42.800
I was excited about it.

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:45.200
I'm not trying to compare; He

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:47.599
used that as a comparison to me. What

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:49.279
I'm doing now, He said it's different,

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:51.200
but it's the same. I'm looking at the

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:53.200
heart. 'But this is not an assignment of toilets, Braden. This is an

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:55.920
assignment—I

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:59.040
know your heart is

00:10:55.920 --> 00:11:02.212
healing evangelism, but

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:04.232
I'm asking you to do something for Me.'And

00:11:02.212 --> 00:11:04.232
I said,

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:11.320
'Yeah.'So

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:11.319
something shifted

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:18.160
and I'm all in now.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:20.560
I knew in my heart,

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:22.160
'Lord, I'll do it until You let me go.'Prayer

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.760
is not a bad thing,

00:11:22.160 --> 00:11:25.839
ladies and gentlemen. I'm not trying to

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:28.160
be a whiner; I'm trying to tell you

00:11:25.839 --> 00:11:30.480
something that I deal with. When

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:32.800
you get real with God, God will get real

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:34.720
with you. You've got to stop pretending

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:38.160
to be what you're not and

00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:40.480
realize that we're all a work in

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:42.240
progress. No matter what level you're at,

00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:45.279
we're all a work

00:11:44.079 --> 00:11:47.040
in progress.

00:11:49.839 --> 00:11:55.040
You might be the

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:56.480
CEO of a company or the

00:11:55.040 --> 00:11:59.279
guy that's the grunt

00:11:56.480 --> 00:12:01.600
getting coffee for the CEO. Whatever

00:11:59.279 --> 00:12:03.200
you do in word

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:05.760
and deed, give all to the glory of God

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:08.800
and give Him praise for it.

00:12:05.760 --> 00:12:10.399
Thank You, Lord, that wherever I'm at in

00:12:08.800 --> 00:12:12.160
this channel and what You've done with

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:13.440
me, I embrace wholeheartedly what

00:12:12.160 --> 00:12:15.760
You've called me to do. I don't

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:18.320
think I'm better than you.

00:12:15.760 --> 00:12:20.319
Humble yourself. You go, 'Well, I

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:22.320
think I want to do this.''But I've

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:24.399
asked you to do this. Don't you realize

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:26.800
that this is so vital to

00:12:24.399 --> 00:12:29.200
the kingdom and to this end-time

00:12:26.800 --> 00:12:31.293
movement? Prayer is the foundation

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:31.440
of

00:12:31.293 --> 00:12:33.680
it.'Maybe

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:37.279
you can relate,

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:38.959
maybe you can't, but I felt I should tell

00:12:37.279 --> 00:12:40.639
you

00:12:38.959 --> 00:12:44.000
because I believe there are so many of

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:45.920
you that struggle with where you are.

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:48.320
You think, 'God, how come I'm still going

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:49.920
around in the wilderness? How come I

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:52.399
keep seeing the backside of

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:54.319
this desert and I keep going around

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:56.560
this

00:12:54.320 --> 00:12:59.519
mountain? I don't understand why I'm

00:12:56.560 --> 00:13:01.359
still facing the giants the way I did five

