glory to glory because I'm

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:09.279
still not yielded to what You've asked

00:13:06.079 --> 00:13:11.439
me to do.'There are

00:13:09.279 --> 00:13:14.160
so many of you

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:16.880
today who could just say,

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:19.120
