00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:24.639
farmer, or mowing grass, or

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:26.800
a school teacher, or

00:13:24.639 --> 00:13:29.360
a librarian—whatever

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:31.920
God has called you to do,

00:13:29.360 --> 00:13:34.560
do everything unto Him with

00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:36.959
all your heart.'Yield yourself over

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:40.479
completely.

00:13:36.959 --> 00:13:43.599
Don't just do it by being

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:46.320
obedient, but be willing and

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:48.160
obedient. When you have a willing heart

00:13:46.320 --> 00:13:50.800
and you're obedient, you'll eat the good

00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:54.959
of the land.

00:13:54.959 --> 00:13:57.920
That's what I had for you today.

00:13:56.639 --> 00:14:01.440
I just want to

00:13:57.920 --> 00:14:02.959
encourage y'all. Be all in. Don't

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:05.680
do

00:14:02.959 --> 00:14:08.560
it half-heartedly.

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:10.160
Don't be divided.

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:14.959
I'm going to

00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:16.480
do what the Holy Ghost has told me to do

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:19.040
today with

00:14:16.480 --> 00:14:21.040
everything I have.

00:14:19.040 --> 00:14:22.719
And when I get on the other side, He's

00:14:21.040 --> 00:14:24.560
going to say, 'Well done, thou good and

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:26.880
faithful servant.'If this is all

00:14:24.560 --> 00:14:28.880
You've got for me, Father, I

00:14:26.880 --> 00:14:30.560
yield to

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:34.959
this mission You have

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:37.040
for me. I give my all to You.

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:44.959
So be all in today.

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:48.900
All right, let's see what

00:14:44.959 --> 00:14:48.900
you have today, son.

00:14:49.839 --> 00:14:54.720
Braden has got some really

00:14:52.639 --> 00:14:57.680
interesting things. Last time when we were

00:14:54.720 --> 00:15:00.079
with you, I saw President Trump

00:14:57.680 --> 00:15:04.160
going to Turkey, and the Lord said,

00:15:00.079 --> 00:15:08.479
'Ungodly alliances.'There'll be ungodly

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:11.040
alliances to pray against—ungodly

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:14.480
covenants

00:15:11.040 --> 00:15:16.639
