00:15:14.480 --> 00:15:19.680
Lord said, 'This man is a tyrant. He's

00:15:16.639 --> 00:15:24.399
evil. He's playing you, Trump.'I

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:27.359
heard

00:15:24.399 --> 00:15:28.959
by the Spirit of the Lord that a

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:31.600
two-state solution would be talked

00:15:28.959 --> 00:15:34.959
about. You're going to hear a two-state

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:39.040
solution pushed very hard. And then I

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:45.920
saw earthquake warnings on the Mississippi River.

00:15:42.079 --> 00:15:48.638
I think it was a 4.2,

00:15:45.920 --> 00:15:50.479
a 3.2, and a 2-point-something that

00:15:48.639 --> 00:15:53.120
are about to happen if they go with the two-state solution.

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:57.759
The Lord said this is a warning.

00:15:53.120 --> 00:16:02.480
Then I saw a hurricane hitting by Mar-a-Lago,

00:15:57.759 --> 00:16:05.680
Miami area. It was a very

00:16:02.480 --> 00:16:08.959
massive storm. When I saw the storm

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:12.880
coming, it was going toward Trump's Mar-a-Lago

00:16:08.959 --> 00:16:16.160
house concerning how you handle

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:18.880
Israel, the

00:16:16.160 --> 00:16:21.040
Promised Land, the Holy Land, and a

00:16:18.880 --> 00:16:23.759
two-state solution. I saw Jared Kushner and

00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:25.439
people that would be influencing

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:28.480
this in the days ahead. The Lord

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:31.519
said, 'Pray,'for I saw an Antichrist

00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:34.240
spirit trying to influence President

00:16:31.519 --> 00:16:36.240
Trump's mind. As you get over there,

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:38.160
you're just kind of in a daze. The Lord

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:40.959
said, 'This is a demonic spirit trying

00:16:38.160 --> 00:16:43.839
to mess with him.'And I saw President

00:16:40.959 --> 00:16:45.439
Trump making ungodly alliances with

00:16:43.839 --> 00:16:47.279
Turkey and others.

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:49.920
I saw

00:16:53.279 --> 00:16:59.600
a ham on a platter that

00:16:56.639 --> 00:17:01.600
had flies on it coming from Trump, and

00:16:59.600 --> 00:17:03.040
this man from Turkey was upset about it. He

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:05.120
said, 'This is the way I want

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:07.760
it to go. Don't let it go the other way. Pray.'So

00:17:05.119 --> 00:17:11.119
this is what we saw.

00:17:11.119 --> 00:17:13.599
Can you play

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:14.079
those clips?

00:17:19.919 --> 00:17:23.559
Play that.

00:17:27.839 --> 00:17:31.600
'Because of the President,

00:17:29.919 --> 00:17:35.360
we have a very good relationship with

00:17:31.600 --> 00:17:36.959
the new leader of Syria, and he's done an

