I don't want him to waste his time

00:18:40.559 --> 00:18:46.240
answering that question because we're

00:18:42.880 --> 00:18:49.039
working very closely with Marco Rubio, a

00:18:46.240 --> 00:18:51.039
very famous man, great Secretary of

00:18:49.039 --> 00:18:52.720
State, and with Scott Bessent and with Pete and everybody else. We're going to be taking the sanctions off. It's time to do that. We don't want to sanction friends. It's very simple.'It's reactive. I can tell you we're going to be taking the sanctions off. I don't want him to waste his time answering that question because we're working very closely with Marco Rubio, a very famous man, great Secretary of State.

00:18:51.039 --> 00:18:54.480
Next.

