would consider. It's a great plane,

00:19:24.960 --> 00:19:31.360
the best plane by far,

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:32.400
and it's certainly something we will

00:19:31.360 --> 00:19:35.719
consider.

00:19:32.400 --> 00:19:35.720
He's

00:19:35.840 --> 00:19:42.639
put

00:19:39.668 --> 00:19:44.559
a lot of money in, especially

00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:47.919
when it's been somebody that

00:19:44.559 --> 00:19:50.960
frankly has been more helpful to the

00:19:47.919 --> 00:19:54.240
United States than many other more

00:19:50.960 --> 00:19:57.280
traditional countries.

00:19:54.240 --> 00:19:58.880
A lot of money.

00:19:57.280 --> 00:20:00.799
Putin, who by the way has a lot of

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:02.400
respect for the President.

