00:20:39.520 --> 00:20:44.559
if you want to keep blessing.

00:20:41.919 --> 00:20:45.120
You said we're trying to end

00:20:45.120 --> 00:20:48.959
eight wars. This one's the

00:20:47.039 --> 00:20:52.720
toughest one. I

00:20:48.960 --> 00:20:54.400
know a lot of people don't

