even close.

00:24:30.799 --> 00:24:35.520
He's a strong person,

00:24:33.111 --> 00:24:37.520
a great leader.

00:24:35.520 --> 00:24:40.320
He's respected by everybody, including

00:24:37.520 --> 00:24:43.440
me, and we're proud to have them

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:45.039
