Look at his eyes; there's

00:25:01.120 --> 00:25:08.360
no soul. He's bad, but he's playing

00:25:05.360 --> 00:25:08.360
everybody.

00:25:09.919 --> 00:25:15.440
Okay, go ahead.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:15.919
And then here's him saying about Iran.

00:25:15.919 --> 00:25:17.440
There's something wrong with the way he

