talk to the press, and they say, "We never

00:25:32.960 --> 00:25:37.957
even talked about it."There's something

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:39.977
wrong with them; they're

00:25:37.957 --> 00:25:39.977
cuckoo.'Liars.

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:44.799
They are. I told you,

00:25:44.799 --> 00:25:50.158
they're liars. They're cheats, they're

00:25:47.840 --> 00:25:53.600
sick people. They've hurt their people.

