00:26:10.400 --> 00:26:17.120
Frankly, I don't want to

00:26:14.480 --> 00:26:19.600
waste my time with them. I'll let

00:26:17.120 --> 00:26:23.879
our wonderful negotiators keep talking

00:26:19.600 --> 00:26:23.879
if they want, but I don't see it.

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:30.799
Is the ceasefire over? Is the

00:26:27.279 --> 00:26:34.799
ceasefire done? Is the deal dead?

00:26:30.799 --> 00:26:37.200
It's a very interesting question. To me,

00:26:34.799 --> 00:26:38.559
I think it's over. I don't want to deal

